      "id": "PopularPost333569",
      "post_content": "@Alphanumerical  \nNot really. One of the best legacy storm decks is based around just ad nausium. If this were an alternate win condition in a deck full of mana-fixing and mana sources that are being drawn/played for free, then why not? You don't need to \\*draw\\* 20 cards, you just need to have\\* 20; and the combo he mentions works.",
