    {
      "id": "PopularPost367640",
      "post_content": "Actually the [ad nauseam](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ad nauseam)+[angel's grace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=angel's grace) combo is not too mana intensive/too hard to pull off. It's an established modern deck, just add in [lotus bloom](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lotus bloom)s and [pentad prism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=pentad prism)s for accel, then a few [simian spirit guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=simian spirit guide)s for mana after you've drawn your deck, and you combo off around turn 4 or 5. The reason this isn't rated higher is because there are 2 superior cards for the kill in that combo, [conflagrate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=conflagrate) and [burst lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=burst lightning), which is the best, as it allows you to combo off and win at instant speed, in response to say, a pact trigger.",
      "posted_by": "Lazrbeams",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost367640\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Actually the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"ad nauseam\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ad nauseam\">ad nauseam</a>+<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"angel's grace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=angel's grace\">angel's grace</a> combo is not too mana intensive/too hard to pull off. It's an established modern deck, just add in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"lotus bloom\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=lotus bloom\">lotus bloom</a>s and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"pentad prism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=pentad prism\">pentad prism</a>s for accel, then a few <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"simian spirit guide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=simian spirit guide\">simian spirit guide</a>s for mana after you've drawn your deck, and you combo off around turn 4 or 5. The reason this isn't rated higher is because there are 2 superior cards for the kill in that combo, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"conflagrate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=conflagrate\">conflagrate</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"burst lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=burst lightning\">burst lightning</a>, which is the best, as it allows you to combo off and win at instant speed, in response to say, a pact trigger.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '367640'); return false;\">\r\n                                   